text: Nodubothea nodicornis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1881. It is known from Colombia and Ecuador.BioLib.cz - Nodubothea nodicornis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1881
title: Nodubothea nodicornis
